For advanced operations, the <%= variable :catalog_name, :platform %> Kibana charts allows using custom init scripts that will be mounted in /docker-entrypoint.init-db. You can use a ConfigMap or a Secret (in case of sensitive data) for mounting these extra scripts. Then use the initScriptsCM and initScriptsSecret values.

~~~
elasticsearch.hosts[0]=elasticsearch-host
elasticsearch.port=9200
initScriptsCM=special-scripts
initScriptsSecret=special-scripts-sensitive
~~~
